^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|First the play. Let's count Vered's tricks. 3 spades, 5 hearts, assuming a 3-2 break, 1 diamond, and 2 clubs for 11 tricks. There is an easy way to guarantee a 12th trick even if spades are 5-2 and that is by ruffing a spade. That will give an extra trump trick.|
