NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at| A second alternative is to retain control in spades and duck a club. That gives a 3rd club trick. I like that alternative even better because if the club finesse works you might even make 7. So Vered can draw trumps as she did, and play a club to the J. That loses, but the @C10 is the 12th trick.|
