NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Granted, if spades break 4-3, she also makes the hand, and that will happen quite often. So she was somewhat unlucky. But either the spade ruff or club finesse are better odds. As I always say, you should get in the habit of counting your tricks for all contracts. That way, when it matters, it will be easier to do.|
