cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Ruffing is a sure thing, finessing is 50-50. But in this case, if you ruff you only make 12 tricks for sure. If you finesse and it loses you make 12 tricks for sure. But if you finesse and it wins, you take 13 tricks perhaps. So on this hand, the finesse is better because you don't really care whether it wins or loses.|
