NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|As to the bidding. First of all, this hand illustrates the value of 2 over 1. Once Vered opens, Cheryl sees slam potential, but is not sure what suit or NT is best. 2 over 1 allows them to bid slowly and easily discover their heart fit. Cheryl did well to bid 4N over 3H. One other very minor point. |
